data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled in the heart of a picturesque neighborhood, offering the perfect blend of tranquility and convenience. This charming 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence boasts an array of delightful features that will enchant every member of your family.  Sip iced tea on your rocking chair FRONT PORCH. Enter into foyer to beautiful GREATROOM with woodburning FIREPLACE the heart of this home. Kitchen includes STAINLESS STEEL appliances, White Cabinetry, GRANITE countertops and nice separate Dining Room (currently used as another living room). Laundry room is large and conveniently located close to primary suite. This home is a SPLIT BEDROOM PLAN. ALL NEW LUXURY VINYL FLOORING IN ALL BEDROOMS AND GREAT ROOM!^  You'll discover the heated and cooled SUNROOM off the Great-Room, a versatile oasis that invites relaxation year-round--use as playroom or WORK FROM HOME OFFICE SPACE.  Step outside onto the covered PATIO AND DECK, where endless opportunities for outdoor enjoyment await. Host summer barbecues, dine al fresco under the stars, or simply bask in the serenity of your surroundings while overlooking the sprawling 1-ACRE +/- FENCED BACKYARD adorned with majestic live oak trees.  With FOUR generously sized bedrooms, including a primary suite with ensuite bathroom with GRANITE countertops, this home offers plenty of SPACE FOR EVERYONE for rest and rejuvenation.   Located just a short stroll away from O'Rourke Elementary School, convenience is at your doorstep. This home offers a sense of seclusion and tranquility that feels like a retreat to the countryside yes super convenient to shopping and dining. Call for appt today!    Don't miss your chance to experience the best of both worlds in this captivating home. Schedule a viewing today and discover the endless possibilities that await in this idyllic retreat.
